    title: "Cafe 24 Park, Bhatiari - Hathazari Link Road",
    body: "Cafe 24 Park is an army-run park in Bhatiari, Chittagong. Cafe 24 Park has located 7 km from Bhatiari to Hathazari and shortly before Chittagong Cantonment. There is a scenic park, a variety of rides, a restaurant serving international quality food items. Cafe 24 Park is a wonderful place to visit and the inside and outside of the park are neat and tidy.\n\nThe equipment used by the army during the training is made for the general public. Visitors will be able to get a good idea using these for a fixed fee. Cafe 24 Park is a complete exception to the rides at traditional children’s parks or amusement parks.",
