    title: "University of Chittagong",
    body: "The University of Chittagong (also known as Chittagong University or abbreviated as CU Bengali: চট্টগ্রাম বিশ্ববিদ্যালয়) is a public autonomous research university in Hathazari in Chittagong, Bangladesh. Founded in 1966, it is the third oldest university in Bangladesh. Its 1,754 acres (710 ha) campus is the largest among Bangladeshi universities.[3]",
